### Product Service API Example Requests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8001
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### 1. List all products (public - no authentication required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/

### 2. List products with pagination (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/?page=1&page_size=10

### 3. Filter products by category (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/?category=Electronics

### 4. Filter products by price range (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/?min_price=50&max_price=200

### 5. Filter products in stock (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/?in_stock=true

### 6. Search products (public endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/search/?q=laptop

### 7. Search with multiple filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/search/?q=wireless&category=Electronics&min_price=20&max_price=100

### 8. Get product by ID (public - no authentication required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/

### 9. Check product stock (public endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/stock/

### 10. Create a new product
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Wireless Bluetooth Headphones",
  "description": "High-quality wireless headphones with noise cancellation",
  "price": "99.99",
  "stockQuantity": 50,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "sku": "ELEC-HEAD-001",
  "isActive": true
}

### 11. Update product (full)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/products/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Product Name",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "price": "89.99",
  "stockQuantity": 45,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "sku": "ELEC-HEAD-001",
  "isActive": true
}

### 12. Update product (partial)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/products/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": "79.99",
  "stockQuantity": 40
}

### 13. Delete product (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 14. Get API documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/docs/

### 15. Get OpenAPI schema
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/schema/

### 16. Get Prometheus metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics/
